ZH: 我们全家又要过节了。
EN: Our whole family is going to celebrate the holiday again.

ZH: 他们每年都要开个大派对来过节。
EN: They have a big party every year to celebrate the holiday.

ZH: 过节很开心，因为可以收到很多礼物。
EN: It's fun to celebrate the holiday because you can receive a lot of gifts.

ZH: 大家都在为过节做准备。
EN: Everyone is preparing for the holiday.

ZH: 过节期间，我们都会去亲戚家串门。
EN: During the holiday, we will visit relatives' homes.

ZH: 你们都准备好过节了吗？
EN: Are you all ready to celebrate the holiday?

ZH: 过节的饭菜总是特别丰盛。
EN: The holiday meals are always especially plentiful.

ZH: 这个节日是我们传统的节日之一。
EN: This holiday is one of our traditional festivals.

ZH: 我们需要买一些过节的礼物。
EN: We need to buy some holiday gifts.

ZH: 过节的时候，街上总是很热闹。
EN: The streets are always lively during the holiday.

ZH: 我们会给亲友们拜年过节。
EN: We will visit friends and relatives to wish them a happy holiday.

ZH: 这是我最喜欢的过节之一。
EN: This is one of my favorite holidays.

ZH: 过节的时候，大家都会穿上漂亮的新衣服。
EN: During the holiday, everyone will wear beautiful new clothes.

ZH: 我们每个人都会感到过节的气氛。
EN: Each of us can feel the festive atmosphere.

ZH: 这个节日是为了庆祝丰收而设立的。
EN: This holiday was established to celebrate a good harvest.

ZH: 我们会在家吃团圆饭过节。
EN: We will have a family reunion dinner at home for the holiday.

ZH: 过节的时候，很多人会去旅行。
EN: Many people will go on a trip during the holiday.

ZH: 这个节日是我们展示文化传统的机会。
EN: This holiday is an opportunity for us to showcase our cultural traditions.

ZH: 过节的时候，我们会放烟花庆祝。
EN: We will set off fireworks to celebrate during the holiday.

ZH: 我们会一起包饺子过节。
EN: We will make dumplings together to celebrate the holiday.
